Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,空…空氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,成為高中生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,655)\fs40}察言觀色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,「空氣」這種行為就不再僅僅是慣用句了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要實際操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,花…小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.08,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子很擅長讓貓親近自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:22:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是貓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠也超級黏榮依子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個 對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
